title: TD Jakes Interview
itunes:title: TD Jakes Interview
description:
Today on the show we had Bishop TD Jakes stop by where he helped us make sense out of the tragic death of Kobe Bryant, finding faith and more. Also, we had business man Steve Stout stop by and speak about signing Kobe Bryant, Dame Dash and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Terry Crews for his comments on the Today show.
